text: What the **** are you doing here?
Come on.
Nonsense, we haven’t finished our drinks.
After you nicked his car, Dean says you’re a fair game.
Listen, boys.
I have had a rather emotional day
so whatever your beef with Egssy is
I would appreciate it enormously if you could just live us in peace
until I finish this lovely pint of Guinness.
You should get out of the way, Grandaddy, or you will get hurt a lot.
He ain’t joking. You should go.
Excuse me.
If you’re looking for another rent boy, they’re on the corner of Smith’s street.
Manners
make a
man.
Do you know what that means?
Then let me teach you a lesson.
Are we going to stand around here all day
or are we going to fight?
